      <title>新世界集团和 Scion 首席执行官在香港房地产市场遭遇困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/hong-kong-property-pain-hits-cheng-dynasty-s-new-world-and-billionaire-scion</link>
