      <title>中国陷入困境的太阳能行业或将迎来转折点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/china-s-troubled-solar-industry-may-be-nearing-a-turning-point</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的太阳能制造商刚刚经历了惨烈的盈利季节，但有初步迹象表明困扰该行业的严重供过于求的局面可能开始缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/china-s-troubled-solar-industry-may-be-nearing-a-turning-point</guid>
